#: The_Shadow_Returns/_main.cfg:41
msgid ""
"This is the story of an age when the glory of Wesnoth had become but a "
"memory of days long past. The fugitive necromancer Gwiti Ha’atel is "
"determined to master the undead hordes and exact his revenge upon the "
"living. His dark journey unleashes waves of power that gradually engulf all "
"of Irdya..."
msgstr ""
"Wesnoth の栄光が遠い追憶の中に消え去った時代の物語。逃亡した死霊術師 Gwiti "
"Ha’atel は、アンデッドの大軍団を支配し、生ける者達に復讐する事を決意した。彼"
"の暗い旅筋は、徐々に Irdya 全てを飲み込む力の波を解き放つ......"

