#. [floating_text]
#. [scenario]: id=04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:462
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:477
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:5
msgid "The Skull of Morgorath"
msgstr "Morgorath の頭蓋骨"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:32
msgid "Move Gwiti himself on all the monoliths"
msgstr "全ての石碑の上に Gwiti を移動させる"

#. [note]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:46
msgid "4 monoliths remaining."
msgstr "4 の石碑が残っています。"

#. [note]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:55
msgid "3 monoliths remaining."
msgstr "3 の石碑が残っています。"

#. [note]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:64
msgid "2 monoliths remaining."
msgstr "2 の石碑が残っています。"

#. [note]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:73
msgid "1 monolith remaining."
msgstr "1 の石碑が残っています。"

#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Karz Gholum
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:116
msgid "Karz Gholum"
msgstr "Karz Gholum"

#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Nakur Kimoni
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:166
msgid "Nakur Kimoni"
msgstr "Nakur Kimoni"

#. [unit]: type=Orcish Warrior, id=Isidal B'Tai
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:204
msgid "Isidal B’Tai"
msgstr "Isidal B’Tai"

#. [side]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:226
msgid "team_name^Morgorath"
msgstr "Morgorath"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:250
msgid ""
"As Gwiti marched along the rugged mountain path, he felt the tingling "
"presence of strange magic weaving through the air, guiding him onward."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:255
msgid "I sense that I am nearing the Skull of Morgorath..."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:257
msgid ""
"Indeed, you are close — but you must perform the ritual to claim your prize. "
"Through your own will and magic, you must awaken the power of the ancient "
"monoliths scattered throughout this land."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:327
msgid ""
"Without my magic, these monoliths remain dormant. Do not squander your time "
"in futile efforts."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:333
msgid ""
"I find it curious that you still hide in the shadows. Have you not the "
"courage to reveal yourself?"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:335
msgid ""
"The time for revelations has not yet come. Trust in the path that lies ahead."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:342
msgid "Are we certain this is the right path? Doubt gnaws at me."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:346
msgid ""
"I share your concern. Only time will tell if the master of the voice speaks "
"the truth or leads us astray..."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:353
msgid ""
"Doubt is a poison that clouds the mind. Embrace your destiny, for it is "
"intertwined with the very fabric of this land."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:356
msgid "I will not succumb to fear. The power I seek is within my grasp!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:360
msgid ""
"Let us hope that we are worthy of the challenges ahead. Our journey is "
"fraught with peril."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:362
msgid ""
"Remember, it is through trials that strength is forged. Prepare yourselves; "
"the monoliths await your call."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. [floating_text]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:375
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:390
msgid "Memoirs of the Dawn"
msgstr "夜明けの回顧録"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:376
msgid ""
"<i>In ages past, our realm knew an epoch of unrivaled splendor. We dwelt in "
"eternal radiance, basking in the golden light of prosperity and glory. In "
"our hubris, we believed our dominion over all living things would endure "
"until the end of time itself. Yet fate proved otherwise, for those who "
"watched from above could not abide such pride.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>遠い昔の時代、我らが領域は比類なき輝きの時代を知っていた。我らは永遠の光明"
"の中に在り、繁栄と栄光の黄金の光の中で生きた。その傲慢さ故に、我らは全ての生"
"ける者への支配が時の果てまで続くと信じていた。だが運命は異なる道を示した。上"
"より見守る者達は、そのような慢心を容認できなかったのだ。</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. [floating_text]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:404
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:419
msgid "Memoirs of the Fall"
msgstr "大堕落の回顧録"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:405
msgid ""
"<i>The Great War raged across eons, until at last we fell from grace. In "
"that cataclysmic hour, both life and void were rent asunder. My own essence "
"was scattered, my form unmade by divine decree, cast adrift from the realm "
"of being.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>大戦は永劫に渡って猛り狂い、遂に我らは恩寵より転落した。その激変の時、生命"
"も虚無も引き裂かれた。我が本質は散り散りとなり、神の裁きにより形すら失い、存"
"在の領域より追放されたのである。</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. [floating_text]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:433
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:448
msgid "Leganoth"
msgstr "Leganoth"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:434
msgid ""
"<i>Yet a fragment of my will remained, sealed within an emissary who walks "
"the mortal realm. In them I placed a shard of my consciousness, and bestowed "
"the ancient knowledge to draw forth my essence from its celestial prison. "
"Upon this vessel of my purpose, I bestowed the name Leganoth.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>だが我が意志の欠片は、死すべき世界を歩む使者の中に封印されていた。我はその"
"者の中に我が意識の破片を宿し、天上の牢獄より我が本質を呼び覚ます古の知識を授"
"けた。我が目的を託したその器に、Leganoth の名を授けたのである。</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:463
msgid ""
"<i>And so I endure in timeless vigil, awaiting the hour when my sundered "
"form shall be made whole once more — when flesh, bone, and spirit shall "
"unite in harmony. Then shall I rise again as Sovereign of Shadow, to claim "
"my rightful dominion. The appointed time draws ever nearer... This truth "
"echoes through the void.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>かくして我は時を超えた見張りの中で耐え忍び、引き裂かれし我が姿が再び一つと"
"なる時を待ち続ける —— 肉と骨と魂が調和の中で結ばれる時を。その時こそ、我は影"
"の君主として再び立ち上がり、正当なる支配権を主張するであろう。定められし時は"
"刻一刻と近づいている...... この真実が虚無を通じて響き渡るのだ。</i>"

#. [then]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:495
msgid "Well done. At last, you have proven yourself to be the chosen one."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:520
msgid "The undead are upon us! To arms, brothers!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:524
msgid ""
"Orcs? It has been too long since I last faced you in battle at Erzen... "
"Soon, your corpses and souls shall litter this battlefield."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:535
msgid "I have fallen to the wicked undead! Avenge me, my kin!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:549
msgid "Dispatch a messenger! Inform our lord of our demise..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:559
msgid "Argh! I meet my end!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:614
msgid "Time drifts by as the air thickens with magic..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:681
msgid "Where in the blazes am I?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:698
msgid ""
"This does not feel like the earth I know... It is as if I am enveloped in "
"pure magic."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:794
msgid "These are not elves... they are mere illusions!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:804
msgid "<i>Is this what I earn for following your guidance?!</i>"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:866
msgid ""
"You have completed the ritual. Now, you must behold the artifact with your "
"own eyes... Yet, the key to the Skull of Morgorath still eludes you. In "
"other words: the doom of the guardians awaits."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:972
msgid "The path to the skull has been revealed!"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:979
msgid "Take the Skull of Morgorath"
msgstr "Morgorath の頭蓋骨を回収する"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:1010
msgid ""
"Argh! This... this is only a half, a mere fragment of the true Skull of "
"Morgorath! Enough of this trickery!"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:1013
msgid ""
"You hold what you need. The true power of Morgorath will only be yours when "
"you face the final trials."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/04_The_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:1021
msgid ""
"Trials? What do you mean by that? I’ve had enough of your twisted games! I "
"am bound by no one, least of all a voice without a face. I fear nothing, but "
"do not think to approach me again!"
msgstr ""

